Daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, an yi nazarin abubuwan da suka biyo bayan karuwar cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) a cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom.
Ta hanyar nuna irin wannan yanayin a cikin EU/Yarjejeniyar Tattalin Arziki ta Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom, ciwon COVID-19 wanda ke da nau'i daban-daban na yaduwar cutar (COVID-19) ya tabbatar da cewa cutar ta COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga gogewar da aka samu daga Italiya, dole ne kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin gaggawa su kara shirye-shirye don karuwar adadin marasa lafiya da suka kamu da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kulawa ta musamman.
A ranar 31 ga watan Disamba na shekarar 2019, an samu rahoton mutane da dama da suka kamu da cutar pneumonia wadda ba a san dalilin da ya sa ta faru ba a Wuhan, lardin Hubei, kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta bayyana cewa, a halin yanzu, sabon nau'in cutar coronavirus da ake kira SARS-CoV-2 shine alamar rashin lafiyar numfashi mai tsanani.
Saboda haka, an sanya sunan SARS-CoV-2 (COVID-19) don rashin lafiyar da ke haifar da kamuwa da cutar.
A cewar shaidun da aka samu zuwa yau, kusan kashi 80 cikin dari na mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 sun kamu da cututtuka masu matsakaici, wato, cututtukan numfashi masu dauke da cutar pneumonia ko babu su, kuma mafi yawansu sun warke.
A cikin kusan kashi 14 cikin 100 na mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, COVID-19 ya zama wani mummunan cuta wanda dole ne a yi musu asibiti, yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin 100 ke fuskantar mummunan rashin lafiya wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti da COVID-19 kusan kashi 4 cikin 100.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom, kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Muna kwatanta yawan mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom da na yanzu a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
An samu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom.
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwa a wurare daban-daban, kuma yanayin annobar COVID-19 a sauran sassan duniya ya kasance a baya da na yanzu.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris na shekarar 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya bayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin mujallar EuroServance na 5 ga Maris, 2020, Spiteri da sauransu sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ma'anar Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO).
A cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai, manyan mutane uku da suka kamu da cutar sun dawo Faransa daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei, China, a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashe 30 na EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom. Saboda haka, a tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an samu kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 a cikin wannan kwanan wata, daga cikinsu, a Italiya kadai, adadin kamuwa da cutar ya kai 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441.
Ana samun bayanan bayanan bayanan da suka biyo baya game da cutar COVID-19.
A Cibiyar Tarayya ta Turai don Rigakafin Cututtuka da Kula da Cututtuka (ECTC), a duk duniya, ana sabunta bayanan da aka samu game da lambobin da aka sanar game da COVID-19 daga ma'aikatar lafiya ta kowace ƙasa, daga hukumomin lafiya na ƙasa da ƙasa da na yanki da kuma Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya a kowace rana a karfe 8 na safe.
An yi amfani da wannan bayanan ne don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/Economics da United Kingdom da kuma kwatanta su da yanayin da ke faruwa a Italiya.
A cikin martani ga yankin da ke da cutar COVID-19 a halin yanzu, mun lissafa jimlar lokutan 14 na mutane da suka kamu da COVID-19 cikin sauri, don haka a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, mun yi la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 a cikin kowace EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom.
