A cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom, yanayin yanayin yanayin COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 na sauri ya bi yanayin lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu ne aka fara samun karuwar COVID-19 a fadin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma Burtaniya, kuma an kara samun karuwar ta a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (subject).
Wannan ya samo asali ne daga saurin karuwar yawan wadanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da kuma United Kingdom sun nuna irin wannan karuwar yanayin a cikin abubuwan da suka biyo bayan COVID-19 (subject).
Hoton 2 ya nuna jimlar adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a lokacin da aka kwatanta da kasashen EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Italiya a lokacin 31 ga Janairu - 15 ga Maris, 2020.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, da misalin karfe 8 na safe, sauran kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma United Kingdom sun riga sun yi rajistar adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar a Italiya, makonni 3 a gaba ko kuma kafin hakan.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 da aka sanar suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma a cikin United Kingdom.
Idan aka duba yanayin yanayin COVID-19 gaba ɗaya, cutar ta bayyana cewa cutar ta ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Wannan ya faru ne duk da cewa, a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, ana amfani da ma'auni daban-daban na kamuwa da cutar, da kuma hanzari don zaɓar marasa lafiya don gudanar da gwajin tabbatar da COVID-19, duk da cewa akwai bambancin tsarin kula da lafiyar jama'a a cikin ƙasa.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci daga yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun ce kusan kashi 10 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 suna bukatar gaggawa.
Bayanai game da COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti da/ko a cikin dakin gaggawa a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matsayin kashi 6% da 1% a matakin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara su cikin tsari don tallafawa bayanan sa ido na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan kamuwa da cutar da mutuwar da aka yi rikodin.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a shekara ta 2010-11 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai tsakanin wuraren da ake yin jinya a Turai, wato, a Jamus, yawansa 29.2 ne ga mutane 100,000, a kuma a Portugal, yawanci 4.2 ne.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasashe na iya samun albarkatu fiye da Italiya (da 12.5 ICU da matsakaiciyar kulawa a kowace 100,000 a 2010-2011).
