Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a sauran ƙasashe sun nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/Yankin Tattalin Arziki na Turai da kuma United Kingdom.
Kasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin gaggawa, suna bukatar su shirya kansu don yanayin da ake fama da cutar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma yawan mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, da kuma yanayin da ake buƙatar kulawa da lafiya, musamman ma a cikin gaggawa.
Kamar yadda ECTC ta bayyana a cikin sabon kimantawar hadarin gaggawa, sauya tsarin kulawa daga na hanawa, da kuma daukar mataki mai karfi da dukkan matakan da za su iya kawo karshen yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 yana da mahimmanci, idan ba a aiwatar da shi a farkon lokaci ba, saurin karuwa da ake tsammani a cikin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci lokaci don fahimtar halin da ake ciki, karɓa, daidaitawa da kuma daukar matakan da suka dace don amsawa.
Saurin kimanta haɗari yana lissafin matakan kiwon lafiya na jama'a da kuma rage tasirin cutar.
Akwai karamin taga na dama, wanda zai iya amfani da shi don ƙasashe su rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, rage rikicin da ke tattare da masana'antar kiwon lafiya, da kuma kara kokarin hana cutar.
Idan ba a yi haka ba, a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa, za a iya fuskantar ci gaban da ke tattare da yawan marasa lafiya da ke bukatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin ƙasashen da suka gaji da EU/Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai.
2019 Cutar coronavirus (COVID-19), cuta mai tsanani ta rashin numfashi (SARS) cuta mai tsanani ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) - ta kashe mutane 3,000 a China da sauran sassan duniya, ta shafi mutane 80,000, kuma ta haifar da bala'i ga mutane.
Kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da SARS-CoV-2 a shekara ta 2003, wanda yake da tsarin tsarin iri ɗaya, SARS-CoV-2 na iya yadawa daga kwayar cutar, kuma yana iya haifar da alamun cutar iri ɗaya a cikin irin wannan aikin.
Koyaya, COVID-19 yana da ƙarancin tsanani da mutuwar fiye da SARS, amma yana da ƙarancin yaduwa kuma yana shafar maza fiye da matasa da tsofaffi da mata fiye da matasa.
Don amsa yawan wallafe-wallafen da ke faruwa game da cutar, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙarin samar da cikakken lokaci da cikakkiyar fahimta game da batun binciken da ke faruwa cikin sauri.
Za mu bincika abubuwan da suka shafi cututtukan cututtuka, yadda cututtuka suka samo asali, ilimin halittu, ganewa, magani, warkarwa, da kuma hana cutar.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ake bukatar amsawa a yanzu, muna fatan wannan bincike zai taimaka mana mu fahimci cutar da ke barazana kuma mu kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara na 25 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda aka tilasta wa duk Sinawa su kasance a gida har tsawon makonni na hutu saboda yaduwar sabon cutar, ya zama abin tunawa da ba a taɓa mantawa da shi ba.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da halaye iri ɗaya da cutar coronavirus (CoV) wanda ya haifar da yaduwar cutar ta SARS a shekara ta 2003, don haka, an sake masa suna SARS-CoV-2 ta Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020.
Cutar ta fara ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin, kuma da sauri ta bazu zuwa kusan kasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19 ya kai 80,000, wanda ya hada da mutane 40,000 da aka kwantar da daga asibiti kuma sama da mutane 3,000 sun mutu.
"Kungiyar lafiya ta duniya (WHO) ta ce COVID-19 ita ce "abokin gaba na farko", kuma ta ce ta fi ta'addanci ƙarfi".
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin kasa da watanni biyu bayan fitowar rahoton farko na gano kwayoyin halitta daga marasa lafiya daban-daban a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, an buga fiye da 200 takardun bincike game da ilimin kwayoyin halitta, cututtukan cututtuka, asalin cututtuka, ganewar asali da magani game da COVID-19.
Wannan bincike na iya taƙaita ci gaban bincike game da sabon abu da ke ci gaba da sauri.
A duk lokacin da zai yiwu, muna gwada COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus, da kuma cututtukan da ke haifar da cutar ta Middle East (wanda ya barke a shekara ta 2012).
