Babban alamar COVID-19 ita ce zazzabi, wanda zai iya kasancewa ba tare da alamun bayyanar cututtuka ba ko kuma yana iya kasancewa tare da bayyanar cututtuka kamar tari, numfashi, ciwon jiki, rashin hankali, ciwon kai, ƙonawa a wuyan, hanci, ciwon kirji, ciwon ciki, kumburi da kuma kumburi.
Wasu marasa lafiya sun sami numfashi da/ko jini a cikin mako guda bayan kamuwa da cutar.
A cikin matsanancin yanayi, marasa lafiya sun sami bayyanar cututtuka na rashin jin daɗi, tashin hankali, acidity na jiki da kuma karuwar jini.
